OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FThe attack in the Kinnaird Avenue area
OL,8,Fof north Belfast on Monday night,
OL,9,Fwhich left a man in his 40s with
OL,10,F"significant injuries to his eyes",
OL,11,Fsparked violent disorder in the
OL,12,FNorthern Irish capital on Tuesday.
OL,14,FThe suspect, a Sudanese asylum seeker,
OL,15,Fis expected to appear in court on
OL,16,FWednesday. Detectives have said there
OL,17,Fis no indication Monday's knife attack
OL,18,Fwas terror-related.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
