OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FAnti-immigration protesters have set
OL,8,Ffire to a bus in the city and
OL,9,Ffirefighters had to remove residents
OL,10,Ffrom their homes in another street
OL,11,Fafter flames spread to properties.
OL,13,FA group of masked males set commercial
OL,14,Fbins alight and pushed them into the
OL,15,FGlider bus on the Newtownards Road in
OL,16,Fthe east of the city on Tuesday
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
