OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FAnti-immigration protests were also
OL,8,Fheld in Glasgow, Edinburgh, Ayr and
OL,9,FAberdeen on Tuesday night in what was
OL,10,Funderstood to be in response to the
OL,11,Fknife attack in Belfast, according to
OL,12,FSTV.
OL,14,FCondemning the wave of violence,
OL,15,FO'Neill said: "Groups of masked men
OL,16,Fburning families out of their homes is
OL,17,Fnothing less than disgusting cowardice.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781165113
OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,F"This has nothing to do with
OL,8,Fcommunity. This is outright thuggery.
OL,9,FThe attack in North Belfast was
OL,10,Fheinous and wrong.
OL,12,F"But there are dangerous attempts to
OL,13,Fexploit that to target and attack
OL,14,Finnocent people who are simply trying
OL,15,Fto live, work and raise their families
OL,16,Fhere.
OL,18,F"Racism, intimidation and violence are
OL,19,Fwrong wherever they occur. There can
OL,20,Fbe no excuse and no justification for
OL,21,Fthese attacks tonight."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
