OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,F"My thoughts are first and foremost
OL,8,Fwith the victim, and I thank the first
OL,9,Fresponders, including members of the
OL,10,Fpublic who intervened."
OL,12,FLater, the leaders of the five largest
OL,13,Fparties at Stormont issued a joint
OL,14,Fstatement in response to the attack.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@WO]
