OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FSinn Fein vice president O'Neill, DUP
OL,8,Fleader Gavin Robinson, Alliance Party
OL,9,Fleader Long, UUP leader Jon Burrows
OL,10,Fand SDLP leader Claire Hanna said they
OL,11,Fwere "united in our condemnation of
OL,12,Fthe horrific incident in North Belfast
OL,13,Flast night".
OL,15,FThe political leaders urged anyone
OL,16,Fwith information that could help the
OL,17,Fpolice investigation to assist
OL,18,Fdetectives, and also issued an appeal
OL,19,Ffor calm on the streets of Belfast.
OL,26,@oD@GrrsD@FOUuD@KO]
