OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FThe victim of Monday's knife attack
OL,8,Fremained in a serious condition in
OL,9,Fhospital on Tuesday receiving
OL,10,Ftreatment for serious eye, face and
OL,11,Fback wounds.
OL,13,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fhas launched a "critical incident" in
OL,15,Fresponse to the incident which was
OL,16,Fcaptured on video and appears to show
OL,17,Fa man stabbing at the victim's head
OL,18,Fand neck while he was lying on the
OL,19,Fground.
OL,26,@vD@POUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
