OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FThe clip shows people, including one
OL,8,Fwith a hurling stick, intervening to
OL,9,Fstop the man attacking the victim in
OL,10,Fthe Kinnaird Avenue residential area.
OL,11,FA kitchen knife was recovered from the
OL,12,Fscene.
OL,14,FEarlier on Tuesday, police revealed
OL,15,Fdetails on the arrested man's
OL,16,Fimmigration status and how he
OL,17,Ftravelled to the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
