OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FHe entered Northern Ireland across the
OL,8,FIrish border in February 2023 having
OL,9,Fflown to Dublin from Paris. The
OL,10,Fsuspect claimed asylum upon arrival
OL,11,Fand in September 2023 was granted
OL,12,Fleave to remain in the UK until 2028.
