OL,3,C'Outright thuggery': Political leaders
OL,4,Ccondemn Belfast riots as homes set
OL,5,Calight
OL,7,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland
OL,8,F(PSNI) Assistant Chief Constable Ryan
OL,9,FHenderson said: "Sporadic pockets of
OL,10,Fdisorder have broken out in a number
OL,11,Fof locations across Northern Ireland
OL,12,Fthis evening, including incidents in
OL,13,Fwhich a number of vehicles have been
OL,14,Fset on fire.
OL,16,F"We are urging everyone to remain
OL,17,Fcalm, act responsibly, and avoid any
OL,18,Factivity that could place themselves
OL,19,For others at risk.
OL,26,@qD@QOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
